5
6 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Appropriation. There is appropriated $5.5 million from the general fund
7 to the department of public health and human services for each year of the biennium beginning July 1, 2025, for
8 the purposes of providing best beginnings child care scholarships to eligible child-care workers as provided in
9 [section 1].
10
11 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Effective date. [This act] is effective July 1, 2025.
